long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Angry Cat loves to practice his artistic moves! Use your shooting skills to propel him through the air through the wooden rings to jump on the stars. Good luck!

How to play

Tap on Angry Cat and aim your catapult for the path to the star. Let go and watch him ascend. Complete the challenge and level up!

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Angry Cat Shoot - Browser game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
